title: please teach me to Play trist and rammus better.
body: I'm looking for higher Elo players who main trist and or rammus to teach me pointers and general game play on them. Also nunu jungle as well. If you can help, would be appreciated. I'd like you to be at least in the 1600 mmr bracket or higher. But not too high that you would complicate the shite outta, wat I should be doing. Thanks in advance.
